title: BRAND NEW CONSTRUCTION 1 Bedroom Apartment on Fawcett St. Avail. 1/1
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 267564036', 'Rent: $3,600 / Month', 'Beds: 2', 'Bath: 2', 'Available Date: 06/01/2022', 'Pet: Pet Friendly', 'Parking:: attached garage', 'ONE MONTH FREE for December 1st', 'Occupancy!', 'Unit 501 at The Brook is a spacious two-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment.', 'Oversized windows let in natural light that spreads throughout the open concept floor plan and warms the Sawyer Mason wide plank wood flooring.', 'The quartz countertops and the GE Café appliance package in the kitchen will please any home chef.', 'A multi-functional kitchen island connects the living and dining area for storage and flexibility.', 'The primary bedroom features an expansive closet with built-in shelving.', 'In the bathrooms, a luxurious shower-tub combo is accentuated with radiant, glossy tiling.', "All residents of The Brook have access to the building's amenities, including a dog wash, bike storage, available garage parking, and a show-stopping roof deck with amazing sunrise/sunset views.", 'Just minutes from the Alewife MBTA station, Route 2, and all that Greater Boston has to offer.', 'Matterport & photos attached of staged model unit #201.', 'See unit floor plan for size and layout of specific unit.', 'FEATURES', 'Bicycle Storage', 'Dog Wash', 'GE Café Appliance Package', 'Garage Parking', 'Quartz Countertops', 'Roof Deck', 'Sawyer Mason Wide Plank Flooring', 'Pictures used in our marketing may occasionally be of model units.', 'Apartment availability, features and amenities subject to variation and change.', 'Contact posting agent for the most current and accurate information available.', '- Senné']
